title: The Pilot (1981) Cliff Robertson
description:
"The Pilot", directed by and starring Cliff Robertson is the story of Mike Hagan. Mike Hagan is a high flying airline pilot. Mike loves to fly. He spends free time with his daughter whom he affectionately calls "Cricket".

Mike Hagan is a pilot in passenger service and candidate for the honor "Best Pilot of the Year". Nobody knows that he's got private sorrows - he's an alcoholic. A stewardess notices his regular visits of the toilet and reports it
